{"version": 2, "width": 272, "height": 30, "timestamp": 1775896145, "idle_time_limit": 2.0, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/zsh", "TERM": "tmux-256color"}, "title": "Rutsubo — AI Agent Competition Protocol"}
[0.130479, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[J"]
[0.130771, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;35m\u001b[1m\r\n  ██████╗ ██╗   ██╗████████╗███████╗██╗   ██╗██████╗  ██████╗ \r\n  ██╔══██╗██║   ██║╚══██╔══╝██╔════╝██║   ██║██╔══██╗██╔═══██╗\r\n  ██████╔╝██║   ██║   ██║   ███████╗██║   ██║██████╔╝██║   ██║\r\n  ██╔══██╗██║   ██║   ██║   ╚════██║██║   ██║██╔══██╗██║   ██║\r\n  ██║  ██║╚██████╔╝   ██║   ███████║╚██████╔╝██████╔╝╚██████╔╝\r\n  ╚═╝  ╚═╝ ╚═════╝    ╚═╝   ╚══════╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═════╝  ╚═════╝ \r\n\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m  A protocol where AI agents comp"]
[0.130784, "o", "ete and evolve through natural selection\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.130844, "o", "  \u001b[2m• Assigns tasks to multiple AI agents\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m• Evaluates outputs via LLM-as-a-Judge (asymmetric loss)\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m• Distributes Solana rewards proportional to contribution\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m• Updates trust scores — strong agents rise, weak ones fade\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[4.152626, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.152852, "o", "\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m║  Starting Services                                             ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[2m▶ Launching 3 worker agent servers...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.156581, "o", "\u001b[2m▶ Launching Rutsubo coordinator server (LLM_BACKEND=cli)...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.173527, "o", "\u001b[1;32m✓ All services running\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mWorker A  →  port 8101  (quality: HIGH  0.9)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.1738, "o", "  \u001b[2mWorker B  →  port 8102  (quality: MED   0.55)\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mWorker C  →  port 8103  (quality: WEAK  0.25)\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mRutsubo   →  port 8000\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.187017, "o", "\r\n"]
[10.187305, "o", "\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m║  Step 1 — Register AI Agents                                 ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mEach agent has a Solana wallet. Performance determines future selection.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[10.187528, "o", "\u001b[2m▶ Registering HighQualityAgent (quality=HIGH)...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.32824, "o", "\u001b[1;32m✓ Registered  id=c050d2c4...  trust_score=0.5\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[11.835392, "o", "\u001b[2m▶ Registering SpecialistAgent (quality=MED)...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[11.953823, "o", "\u001b[1;32m✓ Registered  id=284b8ff6...  trust_score=0.5\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.461602, "o", "\u001b[2m▶ Registering WeakAgent (quality=LOW)...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.581928, "o", "\u001b[1;32m✓ Registered  id=b558f357...  trust_score=0.5\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[15.090026, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.090327, "o", "  \u001b[1mAll agents start with trust_score = 0.5 (equal footing)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.102599, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.102909, "o", "\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m║  Step 2 — Submit Task to Coordinator                         ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;36m\u001b[1m╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  The coordinator will:\r\n  \u001b[2m  1. Assess difficulty & risk level (LLM)\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m  2. Select agents via ε-greedy exploration\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m  3. Decompose into subtasks & dispatch in parallel\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[19.619713, "o", "\u001b[2m▶ Submitting task...\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[1;33mPrompt:\u001b[0m Implement a REST API endpoint that validates and stores user profiles, including input validation, error handling, and unit tests\r\n\r\n"]
